  "3092530": {
    "name": "命运扳机",
    "steam_appid": 3092530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《命运扳机》是一款新次元英雄战术射击游戏。化身能力迥异的「先觉者」，装备强力武器，以枪火之名，重构命运秩序！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投身战术竞技空岛混战，或是团队竞技据点攻防，与队友活用立体地形，制定突袭防守战术，在枪林弹雨中撕开敌方防线，上演策略与枪法的终极对决！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>即刻扣响扳机，击穿次元！</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/ac8d15761bcc7e9c9ee7d8758395908e.poster.avif?t=1771753390\" width=1170 height=1210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/ac8d15761bcc7e9c9ee7d8758395908e.webm?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/ac8d15761bcc7e9c9ee7d8758395908e.mp4?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身个性迥异的炫酷英雄，手握改写战局的超绝技能。或用能量光束一击致命，或借水之力畅爽疾行，或用像素堡垒构筑防御，或优雅释放迷雾，艳杀四方。扣响扳机，让子弹与必杀技在战场上华丽盛放！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/72874bc62437cf15af4692ea6c19e26d.poster.avif?t=1771753390\" width=1170 height=1046 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/72874bc62437cf15af4692ea6c19e26d.webm?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/72874bc62437cf15af4692ea6c19e26d.mp4?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多元玩法火力全开 —— 心跳加速的空岛战术竞技、据点攻防的热血团战、极速缩圈的生死试炼，每一种模式都能点燃你的竞技热血！<br>穿梭在未来幻想风的浮空岛战场，你可以在战术竞技中凭借精准枪法与应变谋略突出重围；<br>投身据点攻防团战，与队友默契配合，制霸核心区域；<br>更能在快节奏刷圈玩法中，直面极速缩圈的压迫感，上演惊心动魄的遭遇战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/003e77fb566e1155fb9266199284279c.poster.avif?t=1771753390\" width=1170 height=1112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/003e77fb566e1155fb9266199284279c.webm?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/003e77fb566e1155fb9266199284279c.mp4?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵活搭配拥有不同定位、身怀绝技的英雄，秀出无数战术可能。与队友默契作战，共同把握进退节奏，打造最强战队。巧用滑翔和载具技能，灵活转移战点，积极寻找芯片强化台，定制升级你的武器。精心策划你的的战术蓝图，你会发现胜利将如同呼吸般自然！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/2a8530242e2beda19fc63d8dc1a95fd3.poster.avif?t=1771753390\" width=1170 height=1052 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/2a8530242e2beda19fc63d8dc1a95fd3.webm?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/2a8530242e2beda19fc63d8dc1a95fd3.mp4?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用最新虚幻引擎5，极致多面3D渲染技术让每个英雄都栩栩如生。在这里，你将感受到枪枪到肉、爽快逼真的射击体验，华丽酷炫的大招演绎、流畅丝滑的移动交互。场景细腻入微，风动草随，所见之处皆触手可及。而你，正是这场白厄生存大电影的主角！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/cf95ae24b196cbf4a2ad6171a6de0647.poster.avif?t=1771753390\" width=1170 height=1190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/cf95ae24b196cbf4a2ad6171a6de0647.webm?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092530/extras/cf95ae24b196cbf4a2ad6171a6de0647.mp4?t=1771753390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受不了了，把作弊的全ban了！先进的AI反外挂技术，为你提供前所未有的安全护航体验；举报、处罚、申诉一条龙迅速响应，还有基于海量作弊样本研发的反作弊策略...无论作弊者如何变换手法，都能被迅速识别打击！</p>",
